com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.auth

接口 AylaAuthProvider

  • 所有已知实现类:
    AylaOAuthProvider, AylaWeChatAuthProvider, BaseAuthProvider, CachedAuthProvider, FaceBookOAuthProvider, GoogleOAuthProvider, SSOAuthProvider, UsernameAuthProvider

    public interface AylaAuthProvider
    An AylaAuthProvider performs the steps necessary to authenticate a user. The AylaAuthProvider object is passed into AylaLoginManager.signIn(com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.auth.AylaAuthProvider, java.lang.String, com.android.volley.Response.Listener<com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.auth.AylaAuthorization>, com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.error.ErrorListener) which will call the authenticate method and listen for the response. The didAuthenticate() response is passed to AylaLoginManager on a successful sign-in operation. The LoginManager at that point will start up the system using the provided authorization credentials.

    • 方法详细资料

      • authenticate

        void authenticate(AylaAuthProvider.AuthProviderListener listener)
        Called by AylaLoginManager, this method should perform the necessary operations to sign in a user. On successful sign-in, the method should call the provided listener via didAuthenticate and provide the AylaAuthorization object with the necessary authenticated credentials. This method should only be called by AylaLoginManager.
        参数:
        listener - The listener to be notified of sign-in success or failure.

      • authenticate

        void authenticate(AylaAuthProvider.AuthProviderListener listener,
                  java.lang.String sessionName)
        Called by AylaLoginManager, this method should perform the necessary operations to sign in a user. On successful sign-in, the method should call the provided listener via didAuthenticate and provide the AylaAuthorization object with the necessary authenticated credentials.
        参数:
        listener - The listener to be notified of sign-in success or failure.
        sessionName - Name of the session for which this authentication is done. This is used for offline mode login

      • updateUserProfile

        AylaAPIRequest updateUserProfile(AylaSessionManager sessionManager,
                                 AylaUser user,
                                 com.android.volley.Response.Listener<AylaUser> successListener,
                                 ErrorListener errorListener)
        Called by AylaSessionManager to update the user profile on the Ayla service or external identity provider service (for SSO users) to match the fields in the provided AylaUser.
        参数:
        user - AylaUser containing the updated user information
        successListener - Listener to receive the updated user when the operation succeeds
        errorListener - Listener to receive an error if something went wrong
        返回:
        the {link AylaAPIRequest} for this operation

      • deleteUser

        AylaAPIRequest deleteUser(AylaSessionManager sessionManager,
                          com.android.volley.Response.Listener<AylaAPIRequest.EmptyResponse> successListener,
                          ErrorListener errorListener)
        Called by AylaSessionManager to delete a user account from Ayla service or the external identity provider (for SSO users).
        参数:
        successListener - Listener called if the operation is successful.
        errorListener - Listener called if an error occurred
        返回:
        the AylaAPIRequest for this operation, which may be canceled

      • signout

        AylaAPIRequest signout(AylaSessionManager sessionManager,
                       com.android.volley.Response.Listener<AylaAPIRequest.EmptyResponse> successListener,
                       ErrorListener errorListener)
        Called by AylaSessionManager to sign out the user.
        参数:
        successListener - Listener to receive the results of the network sign-out call.
        errorListener - Listener to receive an error from the network sign-out call.
        返回:
        the AylaAPIRequest for this command. While the request to sign out from the server may be canceled, the session will be closed regardless.
